sources.title: Bonanza (TV-1960) SHOWDOWN (S2E1)
sources.description:
This Timeless TV Western starring Lorne Green, Pernell Roberts, Dan Blocker and Michael Landon, is one of the most popular shows in television history!

SHOWDOWN: An outlaw gang robs the Virginia City bank. One of the thieves gets hired as a ranch hand at the Ponderosa to keep an eye on the search activity for his gang. The Cartwrights find the new hand friendly and trustworthy--except for Joe, who has his suspicions.
